label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":58,"text":"神经系统疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"高度接触性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"泌尿生殖道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":51,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":56,"text":"神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":24,"text":"冠状病毒属传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎是由冠状病毒属传染性支气管炎病毒引起鸡的一种急性、高度接触性呼吸道、泌尿生殖道、消化道和神经系统疾病。

label: [{"start":8,"end":17,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":34,"text":"冠状病毒属鸡传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":43,"end":49,"text":"呼吸道分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":50,"end":51,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":53,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":54,"end":55,"text":"脾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"血液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":59,"end":62,"text":"腔上囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (一)病原特征：鸡传染性支气管炎病原为冠状病毒属鸡传染性支气管炎病毒，主要存在于病鸡的呼吸道分泌物、肾、肝、脾、血液、腔上囊等。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"酒精","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"乙醚","labels":["drug"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"氯仿","labels":["drug"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"胆盐","labels":["drug"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"一般消毒药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"来苏儿","labels":["drug"]},{"start":54,"end":58,"text":"高锰酸钾","labels":["drug"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"酒精","labels":["drug"]},{"start":67,"end":71,"text":"福尔马林","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎毒耐酸碱，不耐热，对酒精、乙醚、氯仿、胆盐敏感，对一般消毒药均敏感，如1%来苏儿、0.01%高锰酸钾、70%酒精、1%福尔马林，数分钟即可灭活。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎毒血清型较复杂，现已分离出100多个株，已有30种血清型。

label: [{"start":3,"end":12,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"肾病变血清型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":16,"end":22,"text":"呼吸道血清型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"肠型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 现已知鸡传染性支气管炎毒有11个呼吸道血清型，16个肾病变血清型，国外又分离出肠型。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"生殖道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"肠道损伤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"肾病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 除可引发呼吸道、生殖道和肾病变外，还可造成严重的肠道损伤。还有产蛋鸡的变异毒株。

label: [{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"腹泻","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"肌肉病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"呼吸道病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 英国又发现了引起腹泻和肌肉病变而呼吸道病变不明显的毒株。

label: [{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":35,"text":"喉和气管的组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":35,"text":"组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":26,"text":"喉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 我国分离出四个病理型：I型不引起呼吸道症状，只引起喉和气管的组织学变化；

label: [{"start":7,"end":12,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":22,"text":"上呼吸道组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: Ⅱ型引起明显的呼吸道症状及上呼吸道组织学变化；

label: [{"start":4,"end":11,"text":"明显呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":26,"text":"上呼吸道和支气管组织学病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"组织学病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: Ⅲ型引起明显呼吸道症状以及上呼吸道和支气管组织学病变；

label: [{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"间质性肾炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: N型引起所有呼吸道症状与病变以及间质性肾炎。

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"腺胃病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":24,"text":"传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 我国分离到的致腺胃病变的毒株是传染性支气管炎病毒快速变异的结果。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"青年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":16,"end":23,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":37,"text":"变异传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":49,"text":"肾型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":62,"text":"腺胃型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 临床上常见的有引起雏鸡、青年鸡的传染性支气管炎、产蛋鸡的变异传染性支气管炎、幼鸡肾型传染性支气管炎、幼鸡腺胃型传染性支气管炎等。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"变异毒株","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":64,"end":71,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎毒还将会出现很多变异毒株，因此，免疫时用常规的疫苗如Ho、H₂,还有MAs、4/91等，很难奏效，这也是临床上对传染性支气管炎不易治愈的原因。

label: [{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"灭活苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":27,"text":"油乳剂灭活苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 所以，只有临床取样分离毒株制备组织灭活苗或油乳剂灭活苗才见实效。

label: [{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":31,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (二)流行病学特征：仅发生于鸡，其他家禽均不感染，各种年龄的鸡均可发病，但以雏鸡较为严重。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"易感鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":63,"text":"易感鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 主要通过呼吸道排除病毒，经空气、飞沫传给易感鸡，也可通过污染的蛋、饲料、饮水、用具等经消化道感染和垂直传染，传染性极强，易感鸡与病鸡同饲，可于48小时内出现症状。

label: [{"start":31,"end":39,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 过热、严寒、拥挤、通风不良以及营养缺乏等饲养管理不当，均可促进鸡传染性支气管炎的发生。四季均可发生，但以冬季最为严重。

label: [{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (三)临床症状：病鸡常不见前驱症状，突然出现呼吸道症状，并迅速波及全群。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"伸颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"张口","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"喷嚏","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"喘息","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"气管啰音","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"流鼻涕","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":39,"text":"发出特殊叫声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡表现精神沉郁、伸颈、张口、喷嚏、咳嗽、喘息、气管啰音和流鼻涕，发出特殊叫声。

label: [{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"全身衰弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 随着病情发展，病鸡全身衰弱，食欲不振，羽毛松乱，翅下垂。

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"鼻窦肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"流鼻涕","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"多眼泪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"逐渐消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"鼻窦","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 2周龄以内的雏鸡鼻窦肿胀，流鼻涕，多眼泪，逐渐消瘦；

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":10,"text":"产蛋率迅速下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"产软蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 成年鸡产蛋率迅速下降，并产软蛋、畸形蛋等，病愈后，很难恢复到原来的产蛋率。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"侵害肾脏","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"肾炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"肠炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"急性下痢","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":40,"text":"上呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 感染侵害肾脏的毒株时，可引起肾炎、肠炎，并有急性下痢等，有的同时还有上呼吸道症状。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"侵害生殖系统","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"破坏卵巢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"停止发育","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":32,"text":"母雏终身不产蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":41,"text":"成年鸡产蛋率下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"母雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"卵巢","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"生殖系统","labels":["type"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"停产","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 感染侵害生殖系统的毒株时，可破坏卵巢，停止发育，使母雏终身不产蛋，成年鸡产蛋率下降或停产。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"侵害神经系统","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"神经症状","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 感染侵害神经系统的毒株时，可出现与鸡新城疫相似的神经症状。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":40,"text":"感染支原体","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 病程一般1～2周，雏鸡死亡率可达25%,6周龄以上的鸡死亡率低，若继发感染支原体、大肠杆菌时，则死亡率会很高。

label: [{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"鼻窦中有浆液性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"卡他性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":33,"text":"干酪样渗出物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"气囊混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":47,"text":"表面有黄色覆盖物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":66,"text":"小面积的肺充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"鼻窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"气囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":54,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":63,"end":64,"text":"肺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"浆液性","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: (四)病理变化：支气管、鼻腔、鼻窦中有浆液性、卡他性或干酪样渗出物，气囊混浊，表面有黄色覆盖物，在大的支气管周围，可见小面积的肺充血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"液体状的卵黄物质","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"卵泡出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 产蛋鸡腹腔内可见液体状的卵黄物质，卵泡出血、充血、变形；

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":13,"text":"输卵管发育异常","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"发育异常","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 雏鸡有时可见输卵管发育异常。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"侵害肾脏","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"肾脏肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":42,"text":"输尿管常充满尿酸盐结晶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"扩张","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"增粗","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":55,"text":"直肠末端膨大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"膨大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":64,"text":"充满大量石灰样稀便","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"肾小管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"输尿管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":53,"text":"直肠末端","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":63,"end":64,"text":"便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"花斑肾","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":42,"text":"充满尿酸盐结晶","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 感染侵害肾脏的病毒株时，引起肾脏肿大、苍白，呈花斑肾，肾小管、输尿管常充满尿酸盐结晶，扩张，增粗，直肠末端膨大充满大量石灰样稀便；

label: [{"start":6,"end":18,"text":"肝被膜有灰白色尿酸盐沉积","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"肝被膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"心包膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有的心包膜、肝被膜有灰白色尿酸盐沉积；

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"喉头有黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"支气管充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":24,"text":"有灰白色黏性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 喉头有黏液，气管、支气管充血，有灰白色黏性分泌物。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"侵害腺胃","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"腺胃极度肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"极度肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":43,"text":"腺胃壁增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"黏膜水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":65,"text":"腺胃乳头初期水肿发亮","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"水肿发亮","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":68,"end":72,"text":"凹陷破溃","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":75,"end":79,"text":"溃疡出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":82,"end":93,"text":"腺胃乳头可挤出脓性液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":96,"end":108,"text":"腺胃乳头可见肉芽肿样病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":102,"end":108,"text":"肉芽肿样病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":89,"end":93,"text":"脓性液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":109,"end":113,"text":"个体变小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":114,"end":118,"text":"体重减轻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"腺胃壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":82,"end":86,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":96,"end":100,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 感染侵害腺胃的病毒株时，最明显的特征是腺胃极度肿胀，约为正常腺胃的2～5倍，腺胃壁增厚，黏膜水肿、充血、出血，腺胃乳头初期水肿发亮，中期凹陷破溃，后期溃疡出血，有时腺胃乳头可挤出脓性液体，有的腺胃乳头可见肉芽肿样病变。个体变小，体重减轻。

label: [{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"输卵管损害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"损害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":30,"text":"输卵管发育不全","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":37,"text":"失去产蛋能力","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"发育不全","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 感染侵害输卵管的病毒株时，幼鸡的输卵管损害，使输卵管发育不全，失去产蛋能力；

label: [{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"产蛋期推迟","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"产异常蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"减产","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"停产","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"输卵管发育不良","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"发育不良","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"短小","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"管腔变细","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"变细","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"闭塞","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"形成囊泡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":54,"end":57,"text":"壁变薄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":58,"end":64,"text":"内含透明液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"管腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":68,"text":"呈球形","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 如开产前后感染，则产蛋期推迟，产异常蛋，减产或停产，剖检见输卵管发育不良，短小，管腔变细，闭塞或形成囊泡，其壁变薄，内含透明液体，呈球形或柱状。

label: [{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":73,"end":76,"text":"尿囊腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":89,"end":91,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]}]
text: 3.将稀释的各组血清与等量的病毒稀释液混合，于37℃温度下作用1小时(30分钟摇1次)，中和后，每个稀释度的血清接种10日龄鸡胚5～6个，每个鸡胚尿囊腔接种0.2毫升，37℃培养鸡胚6天。

label: [{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"健康鸡胚","labels":["type"]}]
text: 4.同时设已知的阳性血清对照和病毒对照，并设5～6个健康鸡胚对照。

label: [{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":68,"end":75,"text":"特异性病痕鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"失水","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"蜷缩","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"发育小","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 将接种后第2～6天死亡的鸡胚及在6天内仍能存活的鸡胚，但其胎儿具有失水、蜷缩、发育小(接种胎儿重量比健康对照胚最轻胎儿重量少2克以上)等特异性病痕鸡胚的总和计算。

label: [{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]}]
text: 4倍稀释血清组的鸡胚发病和死亡总和达3/5以下者为可疑；

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病毒对照组鸡胚发病和死亡应达到3/5以上。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎病毒各型之间无交又的中和反应，所以上述中和试验只能测知自己所具备的已知的血清型。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"种毒IBV-H","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (二)间接红细胞凝集试验：1.种毒IBV-H是荷兰进口的弱毒株。

label: [{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"尿囊腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"尿囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 2.抗原将毒株接种于9～10日龄鸡胚尿囊腔中，经18~48小时收集鸡胚尿囊液，3000转/分离心30分钟，吸取上清液分装安瓿后冻干，保存于普通冰箱中。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"心脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"枸橡酸钠溶液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 3.兔红细胞无菌操作由兔心脏采血，按1:10加入5%枸橡酸钠溶液抗凝。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":51,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":90,"end":93,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"戊二醛溶液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 4.红细胞醛化将采集的兔红细胞用生理盐水洗涤3次，把沉积的红细胞置冰箱中冷却，用1%戊二醛溶液将红细胞稀释成1%悬液，放于4℃条件下醛化40分钟，不时摇动混匀，然后离心沉淀，沉积的红细胞用生理盐水洗涤5次。

label: [{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"硫柳汞","labels":["drug"]},{"start":39,"end":44,"text":"戊二醛溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":64,"end":70,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":101,"end":104,"text":"戊二醛","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 再用蒸馏水洗涤5次，最后用蒸馏水稀释成30%悬液，加0.01%硫柳汞防腐(1%戊二醛溶液的配制方法：将pH8的0.15摩尔/升的磷酸盐缓冲液1份、生理盐水9份、蒸馏水5份混合后放冰箱中冷却，然后用来稀释戊二醛成1%溶液)。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":27,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":66,"text":"鞣酸溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":90,"end":96,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":108,"end":111,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 5.红细胞鞣化将醛化的红细胞用pH7.2的磷酸盐缓冲液(PBS)洗涤后，配成2.5%红细胞悬液，加等量新配制的1:10000鞣酸溶液，放置于37℃水浴中作用30分钟，用pH7.2的磷酸盐缓冲液洗涤，制成2.5%的鞣化红细胞悬液。

label: [{"start":66,"end":69,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":78,"end":85,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲溶液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 6.致敏将浓缩5倍的抗原(即每瓶分装5毫升抗原，冻干后加1毫升稀释液)3000转/分离心10分钟，吸取上清液1份，加2份2.5%鞣化红细胞和2份pH6.4的磷酸盐缓冲溶液，在37℃水浴中作用30分钟，1000转/分离心3分钟。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":19,"text":"明胶磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":57,"end":60,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":46,"text":"明胶磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 沉积的红细胞用0.4%明胶磷酸盐缓冲液处理10分钟，离心沉淀后，再用0.4%明胶磷酸盐缓冲液制成1%或2.5%致敏红细胞悬液备用。

label: [{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"尿囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"健康鸡胚","labels":["type"]}]
text: 对照用的健康鸡胚尿囊液和鞣化红细胞在同样条件处理。

label: [{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"免疫鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"健康鸡","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 7.血清健康鸡血清为阴性血清，免疫鸡的血清为阳性血清。

label: [{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 8.试验操作：(1)白瓷板法2.5%的致敏红细胞和血清按1:1滴入，充分振荡均匀，在20～25℃温度下经2分钟后判定。

label: [{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":55,"text":"明胶磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":57,"end":61,"text":"健康尿囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":64,"end":67,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":79,"end":82,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":105,"end":108,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":126,"end":129,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":72,"end":76,"text":"健康尿囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 同时设下列各组对照：鞣化红细胞对照组(即鞣化红细胞加被检血清)、致敏红细胞对照组(即致敏细胞加明胶磷酸盐缓冲液)、健康尿囊液致敏红细胞对照组(即健康尿囊液致敏红细胞加被检血清)、阳性血清对照组(即阳性血清加致敏红细胞)、阴性血清对照组(即阴性血清加致敏红细胞)。

label: [{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 判定结果：#：红细胞凝集成颗粒，细胞周围液体清晰。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: +++：红细胞凝集成颗粒，但比上者小，周围液体清晰。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: ++:红细胞凝集成颗粒，周围液体稍有混浊。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: +：红细胞呈小颗粒状凝集，周围液体混浊。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: -：红细胞不凝集，呈均质状态沉下。

label: [{"start":28,"end":34,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":61,"end":64,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)聚氯乙烯微量塑料板法将供试验用的血清用pH7.2的磷酸盐缓冲液2倍递减稀释，每孔0.025毫升，然后加2.5%的致敏红细胞0.025毫升，用微量搅拌振荡器振荡30～60秒，在20~25℃温度下，2小时后判定结果。

label: [{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 判定结果：#:孔底呈均匀状态，无红细胞沉下。

label: [{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: +++:孔底有少许下沉的红细胞，周围呈均质状态。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: ++:红细胞下沉比上者大，周围呈均质状态。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: +：孔底有红细胞沉积，周围液体稍有混浊。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: ±：孔底有红细胞沉积，周围液体比上者清晰。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: -:孔底红细胞沉积，周围液体清晰。

label: [{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"严格执行检疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"隔离","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":32,"text":"鸡舍要保温","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"通风换气","labels":["control"]},{"start":38,"end":42,"text":"防止拥挤","labels":["control"]},{"start":43,"end":49,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]}]
text: 三、防制措施：严格执行检疫、隔离、消毒等卫生防疫措施，鸡舍要保温，通风换气，防止拥挤，加强饲养管理，增强机体抗病能力。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"按时接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"正确使用疫苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":13,"end":21,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"滴鼻","labels":["control"]},{"start":69,"end":80,"text":"传染性支气管炎Hs₂苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":42,"end":53,"text":"传染性支气管炎H₁2₀","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 按时接种和正确使用疫苗，对鸡传染性支气管炎防制有一定作用，40日龄之内在适当时机先用传染性支气管炎H₁2₀滴鼻首免，60日龄后在适当时机用传染性支气管炎Hs₂苗饮水二免，于110日龄时再用苗重免。

label: [{"start":3,"end":13,"text":"肾型传染性支气管炎苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"肾株病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 现用的肾型传染性支气管炎苗对预防肾株病毒感染有较好的保护作用，可按厂家说明使用。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":25,"text":"高度接触性呼吸道疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎是鸡的一种急性、高度接触性呼吸道疾病。

label: [{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"喷嚏","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"流鼻液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"产蛋量减少","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":31,"text":"呼吸道黏膜呈浆液性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":37,"text":"卡他性炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"呼吸道黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"浆液性","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 以咳嗽，喷嚏。雏鸡流鼻液，产蛋鸡产蛋量减少，呼吸道黏膜呈浆液性、卡他性炎症为特征。

label: [{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"支原体病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":16,"text":"大肠杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"葡萄球菌病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 常继发或并发支原体病、大肠杆菌病、葡萄球菌病等，导致死淘率增加，还常被漏诊、误诊。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":47,"end":55,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎病原的血清型较多，新的血清型不断出现，加上不适当的免疫程序，常导致免疫失败，使鸡传染性支气管炎不能得到有效控制，给养鸡业造成了巨大损失。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":12,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎仅发生于鸡，其他家禽均不感染。

label: [{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":36,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 各种年龄的鸡都可发病，但雏鸡最为严重，死亡率也高，一般以40日龄以内的鸡多发。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"易感鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎主要经呼吸道传染，病毒从呼吸道排毒，通过空气的飞沫传给易感鸡。

label: [{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 也可通过被污染的饲料、饮水及饲养用具经消化道感染。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎一年四季均能发生，但以冬春季节多发。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"维生素","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 鸡群拥挤、过热、过冷、通风不良、温度过低、缺乏维生素和矿物质，以及饲料供应不足或配合不当。

label: [{"start":4,"end":11,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 均可促使传染性支气管炎发生。

label: [{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"呼吸型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)呼吸型：病鸡无明显的前驱症状，常突然发病，出现呼吸道症状，并迅速波及全群。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"幼雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"伸颈","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"张口呼吸","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"咕噜","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 幼雏表现为伸颈、张口呼吸、咳嗽有“咕噜”音，尤以夜间最清楚。

label: [{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"精神萎靡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"食欲废绝","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"昏睡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"怕冷","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":33,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 随着病情的发展，全身症状加剧。病鸡精神萎靡，食欲废绝、羽毛松乱、翅下垂、昏睡、怕冷。

label: [{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"病雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"鼻窦肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"流黏性鼻液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"流泪","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"甩头","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"鼻窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":42,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 常拥挤在一起。两周龄以内的病雏鸡，还常见鼻窦肿胀、流黏性鼻液、流泪等症状，病鸡常甩头。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"产蛋量下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"产软壳蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 产蛋鸡感染后产蛋量下降25%~50%,同时产软壳蛋、畸形蛋。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"肾型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"肾型支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (2)肾型：感染肾型支气管炎病毒后其典型症状分3个阶段。

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":17,"text":"轻微呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":38,"text":"气管发出啰音","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"啰音","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"打喷嚏","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 第1个阶段是病鸡表现轻微呼吸道症状，鸡被感染后24~48小时开始气管发出啰音，打喷嚏及咳嗽，并持续1~4天。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":2,"end":7,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 这些呼吸道症状一般很轻微。有时只在晚上安静的时候才听得比较清楚，因此常被忽视。

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":18,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":39,"end":44,"text":"受感染鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 第2个阶段是病鸡表面康复，呼吸道症状消失，鸡群没有可见的异常表现。第3个阶段是受感染鸡群突然发病，并于2~3天逐渐加剧。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"挤堆","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"厌食","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"排白色稀便","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":24,"text":"粪便中几乎全是尿酸盐","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡挤堆、厌食，排白色稀便，粪便中几乎全是尿酸盐。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"呼吸型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":24,"text":"肺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"呼吸器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"气管环出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":52,"text":"管腔中有黄色或黑黄色栓塞物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":49,"text":"黑黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":52,"text":"栓塞物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"气管环","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"管腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)呼吸型。主要病变见于气管、支气管、鼻腔、肺等呼吸器官。表现为气管环出血，管腔中有黄色或黑黄色栓塞物。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"幼雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"鼻窦黏膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":21,"text":"鼻腔中有黏稠分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"黏稠分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"鼻窦黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"肺脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"肺脏水肿","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 幼雏鼻腔、鼻窦黏膜充血，鼻腔中有黏稠分泌物，肺脏水肿或出血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"患鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"输卵管发育受阻","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"发育受阻","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"变细","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"变短","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"成囊状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"卵泡变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"破裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 患鸡输卵管发育受阻，变细、变短或成囊状。产蛋鸡的卵泡变形，甚至破裂。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"肾型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"肾脏肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"呈苍白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":26,"text":"肾小管充满尿酸盐结晶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"尿酸盐结晶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"扩张","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":37,"text":"外形呈白线网状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"花斑肾","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"肾小管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)肾型。肾脏肿大，呈苍白色；肾小管充满尿酸盐结晶，扩张，外形呈白线网状，俗称“花斑肾”。

label: [{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"尿酸盐沉着","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"心包","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"腹腔脏器","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 严重的病例在心包和腹腔脏器表面均可见白色的尿酸盐沉着。

label: [{"start":5,"end":12,"text":"法氏囊黏膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":27,"text":"囊腔内积有黄色胶冻状物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"胶冻状物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":10,"text":"法氏囊黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"囊腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有时还可见法氏囊黏膜充血、出血，囊腔内积有黄色胶冻状物；

label: [{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"肠黏膜呈卡他性炎变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"卡他性炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":20,"text":"全身皮肤和肌肉发绀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"发绀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"肌肉失水","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"全身皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"失水","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 肠黏膜呈卡他性炎变化；全身皮肤和肌肉发绀，肌肉失水。

label: [{"start":3,"end":15,"text":"传染性支气管炎病毒变异株","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":31,"text":"胸深肌组织苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"胶冻样水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":45,"text":"胴体外观湿润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":56,"text":"输卵管黏膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":57,"end":62,"text":"气管环充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":29,"text":"胸深肌组织","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"胴体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":54,"text":"输卵管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":57,"end":60,"text":"气管环","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (3)传染性支气管炎病毒变异株。特征性变化表现为胸深肌组织苍白，呈胶冻样水肿，胴体外观湿润，卵巢、输卵管黏膜充血、气管环充血、出血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"降低饲养密度","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"避免鸡群拥挤","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"注意温度","labels":["control"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"避免过冷","labels":["control"]},{"start":39,"end":43,"text":"加强通风","labels":["control"]},{"start":44,"end":55,"text":"防止有害气体刺激呼吸道","labels":["control"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 加强饲养管理。降低饲养密度，避免鸡群拥挤，注意温度、湿度变化，避免过冷、过热。加强通风，防止有害气体刺激呼吸道。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"合理搭配饲料","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"维生素A","labels":["drug"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"维生素","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 合理搭配饲料，防止维生素尤其是维生素A的缺乏，以增强机体的抵抗力。

label: [{"start":1,"end":7,"text":"适时接种疫苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":9,"end":19,"text":"呼吸型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"点眼","labels":["control"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"滴鼻","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":48,"text":"传染性支气管炎H120弱毒疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: ②适时接种疫苗。对呼吸型传染性支气管炎，首次免疫可在7~10日龄用传染性支气管炎H120弱毒疫苗点眼或滴鼻；

label: [{"start":9,"end":23,"text":"传染性支气管炎H52弱毒疫苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"滴鼻","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"点眼","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 二免可于30日龄用传染性支气管炎H52弱毒疫苗点眼或滴鼻；

label: [{"start":4,"end":17,"text":"传染性支气管炎灭活油乳疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"肌内注射","labels":["control"]}]
text: 开产前用传染性支气管炎灭活油乳疫苗肌内注射，每只0.5mL。

label: [{"start":1,"end":10,"text":"肾型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":39,"text":"肾型传染性支气管炎弱毒苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]}]
text: 对肾型传染性支气管炎。可于4~5日龄和20~30日龄用肾型传染性支气管炎弱毒苗进行免疫接种。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"灭活油乳疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"颈部皮下注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"颈部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 或用灭活油乳疫苗于7~9日龄颈部皮下注射。

label: [{"start":2,"end":14,"text":"传染性支气管炎病毒变异株","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"弱毒疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":52,"end":58,"text":"灭活油乳疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":45,"end":52,"text":"皮下及肌内注射","labels":["control"]}]
text: 而对传染性支气管炎病毒变异株，可于20~30日龄、100～120日龄接种4/91弱毒疫苗或皮下及肌内注射灭活油乳疫苗。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":27,"text":"改善饲养管理条件","labels":["control"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎目前尚无特异性治疗方法，改善饲养管理条件。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"降低鸡群密度","labels":["control"]},{"start":10,"end":18,"text":"饮水中添加抗生素","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"抗生素","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 降低鸡群密度，饲料或饮水中添加抗生素对防止继发感染具有一定的作用。

label: [{"start":1,"end":9,"text":"肾型传染性气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":24,"text":"降低饲料中蛋白的含量","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":33,"text":"注意补充钾和钠","labels":["control"]}]
text: 对肾型传染性气管炎，发病后应降低饲料中蛋白的含量，并注意补充钾和钠，具有一定的治疗作用。
